Title: Lacuna
Plot: A surprise guest shows up at a sad event as Bette gets stunning news about her job. Tina goes into a surprisingly difficult labor, Jenny finally reaches breaking point over her painful childhood memory, Alice struggles with her jealousy, and Peggy Peabody lays down the laws with her daughter, Helena.
GuestStars: Nadine States,  Candus Churchill,  Georgia Craig,  Lovie Eli,  Marcus Mosely,  Will Sanders,  Debbie Shair,  Michael Inez,  Craig Bartock,  Tom Pickett,  Ann Wilson,  Benjamin Smith,  Ted
